description: Hello! My Wife Christina and I are glad you are visiting Kona Ice North Garland! We are a mobile food truck and we serve premium Hawaiian shaved Ice. We have over 50 flavors. No event is too big or too small. So please follow us to find out where we are, or invite us to bring you some delicious Konas! We will bring them to you! We would love to come to your company and treat everyone. We also love to help schools and organizations fundraise so ask us about that. We operate in Garland, Plano, Murphy, and Richardson. Thank you and we look forward to hearing from you!
name: Kona Ice North Garland
